{
    "type": "script",
    "id": "8e10fd6f-6332-485b-957d-1c82efe58d1d",
    "name": "LT10: Aftermath of the Dead",
    "sceneId": "981ec865-3e1b-4f3e-bb0d-11df2bc7d593",
    "actorId": "bdddd1b1-bbf3-4dd5-bbd6-0ef3115d8b66",
    "trigger": {
        "type": "triggers.manual",
        "name": "Manual"
    },
    "entryPoints": [
        {
            "type": "scripts.entryPoint",
            "id": "79cf6483-8ad3-418c-bb34-73d548b8cfc5",
            "name": "Main",
            "nodes": [
                {
                    "type": "nodes.showMenu",
                    "id": "a4e6db5f-91fb-4567-8ed8-a42f921788b6",
                    "options": [
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "d093755f-84e4-4d40-8239-40294a253f30",
                            "text": "Ask About Thomas",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "3055a7b6-d3cc-4972-9eb2-7622a7ca1441",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "bdddd1b1-bbf3-4dd5-bbd6-0ef3115d8b66",
                                    "text": "How are you today?",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "ea03daed-fdf7-400f-b65b-4c26b11763bb",
                                    "actorId": "bdddd1b1-bbf3-4dd5-bbd6-0ef3115d8b66",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Now that I've spoken with my father, I'm feeling very relieved. I didn't realize how much my guilt about being a Rogue rather than a Paladin was weighing on me. ",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "3",
                            "ExitMenu": false
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "ad80d3b7-ccd8-4ad7-8f4a-773f7e3af48b",
                            "text": "Ask About Thomas' Father",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "e95f9906-e7f4-4256-9898-173011c24749",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "bdddd1b1-bbf3-4dd5-bbd6-0ef3115d8b66",
                                    "text": "Your father must have been a great hero. That was an impressive memorial.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "025ec59c-806b-4df0-9157-bd63329b1181",
                                    "actorId": "bdddd1b1-bbf3-4dd5-bbd6-0ef3115d8b66",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "He was knighted for his bravery by the King of Kent in Albion - you can see that on one of the murals in the memorial. He fought the dragon shown on the other mural here in Sardonia.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "f7bce0e3-b791-4c6c-9712-6c93137e0441",
                                    "actorId": "bdddd1b1-bbf3-4dd5-bbd6-0ef3115d8b66",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "My father has always been my hero. I didn't realize how much of a hero he was to other people.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "4",
                            "ExitMenu": false
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "b71627e4-85ee-487a-9874-f1f9f0d64894",
                            "text": "Ask About Books",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "9d8d54b7-df01-479c-a491-98230599fe2d",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "bdddd1b1-bbf3-4dd5-bbd6-0ef3115d8b66",
                                    "text": "So are there any books written about your father?",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                    "id": "6d257275-aae2-43ac-8067-02b0ac793929",
                                    "actorId": "bdddd1b1-bbf3-4dd5-bbd6-0ef3115d8b66",
                                    "amount": "5",
                                    "change": "1",
                                    "notify": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "00bb48b9-a8f4-4d64-a0a8-47f61e39b2b3",
                                    "actorId": "bdddd1b1-bbf3-4dd5-bbd6-0ef3115d8b66",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Paladins don't like publicity. My father would have been shocked if he realized how fancy the Paladin memorial was. He would have preferred a simple plaque.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "4",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "8bc413aa-71e0-4e08-b0fa-0b1fa12ee34d",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "bdddd1b1-bbf3-4dd5-bbd6-0ef3115d8b66",
                                    "text": "Why do Paladins avoid publicity? I mean, people love hearing about heroic deeds. ",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "11535a43-2e0b-4bc6-9eb1-8801e41b1d31",
                                    "actorId": "bdddd1b1-bbf3-4dd5-bbd6-0ef3115d8b66",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "I think it's because Paladins see themselves as servants of Justice. They don't seek glory or gold - they seek to do what must be done for the good of all.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "58e431ab-dee3-4c2f-a109-05e1a71c8a17",
                                    "actorId": "bdddd1b1-bbf3-4dd5-bbd6-0ef3115d8b66",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "When my father was home, he liked to spend quiet evenings helping me with my lessons or telling me about the lands he had visited. He seldom spoke about his missions or deeds.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "a45932b1-3322-4e5f-bc38-f5de57d7d308",
                                    "actorId": "bdddd1b1-bbf3-4dd5-bbd6-0ef3115d8b66",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "In some ways I guess, Paladins are like Rogues. They don't want to call attention to themselves. They just want to accomplish their goals. ",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "10",
                            "ExitMenu": false
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "547a5283-20e1-4857-9d24-f972a5e71c48",
                            "text": "Flirt With Thomas",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "1c0ee7c2-2f59-4aa0-8473-45f5a910c5aa",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "bdddd1b1-bbf3-4dd5-bbd6-0ef3115d8b66",
                                    "text": "You know, we really need to get together more often - preferably not in the cold depths of the catacombs. ",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.branch",
                                    "sections": [
                                        {
                                            "type": "nodes.branchSection",
                                            "expression": {
                                                "type": "expressions.inTags",
                                                "scope": "scene",
                                                "scopeId": "25782df1-4461-4651-9bab-1fb4e1b4e366",
                                                "scopeFilterId": null,
                                                "tags": "hadThomasTalkThanks",
                                                "has": false
                                            },
                                            "nodes": [
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "149d47f8-dce9-4f80-8d6a-565d02a6fbc0",
                                                    "actorId": "bdddd1b1-bbf3-4dd5-bbd6-0ef3115d8b66",
                                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "text": "Actually, I'd like to talk with you more later tonight. Could you please meet me after curfew in Darla's Room?",
                                                    "emotion": "0",
                                                    "emotion2": "4",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.showMenu",
                                                    "id": "d9d9a367-78ec-42b8-8c46-210ed83b6ca5",
                                                    "options": [
                                                        {
                                                            "type": "options.text",
                                                            "id": "1d5eb600-3abc-4332-b06f-ff96329073c4",
                                                            "text": "Agree to Meet",
                                                            "nodes": [
                                                                {
                                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                                    "id": "5b0d37f5-310f-4d0c-8088-8c3accc16468",
                                                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                                    "actorId2": "bdddd1b1-bbf3-4dd5-bbd6-0ef3115d8b66",
                                                                    "text": "Sure, I'd be happy to get to know you better tonight.",
                                                                    "emotion": "1",
                                                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                                                    "device": "0",
                                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                                },
                                                                {
                                                                    "type": "nodes.addJournalEntry",
                                                                    "id": "29d43bc1-3715-492a-80ed-f937aa180f93",
                                                                    "name": "A Tryst with Thomas",
                                                                    "notify": false,
                                                                    "description": "Thomas... or Janet... wants to talk later tonight in Darla's room. This should be interesting."
                                                                },
                                                                {
                                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                                    "id": "801429da-0809-4345-bf20-59d7634a2832",
                                                                    "actorId": "bdddd1b1-bbf3-4dd5-bbd6-0ef3115d8b66",
                                                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                                    "text": "Thanks. I'll see you later, then.",
                                                                    "emotion": "1",
                                                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                                                    "device": "0",
                                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                                },
                                                                {
                                                                    "type": "nodes.changeTags",
                                                                    "id": "79e46625-11ab-428b-97ed-8527c52501a9",
                                                                    "scope": "actor",
                                                                    "scopeId": "bdddd1b1-bbf3-4dd5-bbd6-0ef3115d8b66",
                                                                    "scopeFilterId": null,
                                                                    "tagsToAdd": "DarlaDate",
                                                                    "tagsToRemove": null
                                                                }
                                                            ],
                                                            "expression": null,
                                                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                                                            "minutes": "2",
                                                            "ExitMenu": true
                                                        },
                                                        {
                                                            "type": "options.text",
                                                            "id": "fb7b554f-b8de-4d8c-97d2-1de037c9ddf7",
                                                            "text": "Decline to Meet",
                                                            "nodes": [
                                                                {
                                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                                    "id": "02c44f72-f6a9-49eb-b45e-838c92c36052",
                                                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                                    "actorId2": "bdddd1b1-bbf3-4dd5-bbd6-0ef3115d8b66",
                                                                    "text": "Sorry, but I have other plans for tonight.",
                                                                    "emotion": "0",
                                                                    "emotion2": "2",
                                                                    "device": "0",
                                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                                },
                                                                {
                                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                                    "id": "11cbd387-cb75-4f17-999c-054cb777dab2",
                                                                    "actorId": "bdddd1b1-bbf3-4dd5-bbd6-0ef3115d8b66",
                                                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                                    "text": "Ah, well, thanks, anyway.",
                                                                    "emotion": "2",
                                                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                                                    "device": "0",
                                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                                }
                                                            ],
                                                            "expression": null,
                                                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                                                            "minutes": "2",
                                                            "ExitMenu": true
                                                        }
                                                    ],
                                                    "AutoAddDone": false,
                                                    "Unique": true
                                                }
                                            ]
                                        },
                                        {
                                            "type": "nodes.branchSection",
                                            "expression": null,
                                            "nodes": [
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "f4e61cf2-9f47-4d75-87c2-993cf9ed6981",
                                                    "actorId": "bdddd1b1-bbf3-4dd5-bbd6-0ef3115d8b66",
                                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "text": "Or in stuffy old libraries?",
                                                    "emotion": "1",
                                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "3ab8ee12-137d-483e-a726-009a6cb47cb0",
                                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "actorId2": "bdddd1b1-bbf3-4dd5-bbd6-0ef3115d8b66",
                                                    "text": "Particularly not in stuffy libraries. ",
                                                    "emotion": "1",
                                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "e919b4de-323e-49f6-a910-9b484fe9cd7c",
                                                    "actorId": "bdddd1b1-bbf3-4dd5-bbd6-0ef3115d8b66",
                                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "text": "I suppose I could take a break from my studies to walk around the Courtyard for a bit - with you.",
                                                    "emotion": "1",
                                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "7da0e06b-7033-4e1e-9e1b-f9f7aa351096",
                                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "actorId2": "bdddd1b1-bbf3-4dd5-bbd6-0ef3115d8b66",
                                                    "text": "Well then, I just happen to have a Courtyard close at hand for us to walk around.",
                                                    "emotion": "1",
                                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.fade",
                                                    "scope": "FadeOutAndIn",
                                                    "fadeTime": 0.5,
                                                    "fadeTime2": 2,
                                                    "wait": true,
                                                    "fadeDown": 0.5,
                                                    "fadeColorR": 0,
                                                    "fadeColorG": 0,
                                                    "fadeColorB": 0
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.onceDaily",
                                                    "id": "d26e6e5a-d8e0-407d-a3f5-ff55e8bda6b5",
                                                    "nodes": [
                                                        {
                                                            "type": "nodes.incrementTime",
                                                            "id": "13257dd3-fefe-40c5-a752-8654c5927bd2",
                                                            "days": 0,
                                                            "hours": 0,
                                                            "minutes": "20"
                                                        }
                                                    ]
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                                    "id": "a7fb450a-424e-49df-b19d-b2b79c9e43e5",
                                                    "actorId": "bdddd1b1-bbf3-4dd5-bbd6-0ef3115d8b66",
                                                    "amount": "5",
                                                    "change": "1",
                                                    "notify": true
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "bb424b6f-e597-462b-905e-54cea7222394",
                                                    "actorId": "bdddd1b1-bbf3-4dd5-bbd6-0ef3115d8b66",
                                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "text": "Thanks, Shawn, we should do this more often... spend time together, that is.",
                                                    "emotion": "1",
                                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "abab00b7-3e05-4262-83ca-c48e1cca2aee",
                                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "actorId2": "bdddd1b1-bbf3-4dd5-bbd6-0ef3115d8b66",
                                                    "text": "I look forward to it.",
                                                    "emotion": "1",
                                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                }
                                            ]
                                        }
                                    ]
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "6",
                            "ExitMenu": false
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "0f02a0af-49b1-4e0d-8123-9960e79ffdc8",
                            "text": "Say Goodbye",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "f57a0ed0-9792-4995-a467-58b18738fdc2",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "bdddd1b1-bbf3-4dd5-bbd6-0ef3115d8b66",
                                    "text": "See you later!",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "229ecc5d-6908-48e1-83a0-8480b2c5cab9",
                                    "actorId": "bdddd1b1-bbf3-4dd5-bbd6-0ef3115d8b66",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "I look forward to it.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": true,
                            "minutes": "5",
                            "ExitMenu": true
                        }
                    ],
